<i>noun</i>: 사욕 [사욕], 사심 [사심], 사리사욕 [사리사욕] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사욕 [사욕]</dt><br>
<dd>selfish desire; self-interest</dd><br>
<dd>자신의 개인적인 이익만을 채우려는 욕심.</dd><br>
<dd>A desire to pursue one's own personal interest.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사심 [사심]</dt><br>
<dd>ulterior motive; being selfish; self-interest</dd><br>
<dd>개인적이고 사사로운 마음. 또는 자기의 욕심을 채우려는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of mind pursuing personal and private purposes, or fulfilling a selfish desire.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사리사욕 [사리사욕]</dt><br>
<dd>self-interest; selfish desire</dd><br>
<dd>개인적인 이익과 욕심.</dd><br>
<dd>A desire and greed for personal gain.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>